{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"fdc972f641","title":"对贺诚来信的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c0978cf676","index":0,"year":1972,"month":6,"day":28,"articleId":"fdc972f641"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji51","name":"毛泽东全集第51卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/51-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji51":{"comments":[{"id":"3d47d5eb97","publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"fdc972f641","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"贺诚，原任中国人民解放军军事医学科学院院长。“文化大革命”中受到林彪反革命集团的追害。1972年6月26日，他给毛泽东写信，要求分配工作。毛泽东阅信后写了这个批语。接到毛泽东批示后，中国人民解放军总政治部曾建议贺诚任总后勤部副部长，于1973年1月17日上报中央军委，军委办公会议各同志圈阅后在1973年8月退回总政。1975年3月22日，贺诚的女儿贺礼荣再次写信，要求给其父分配工作。毛泽东阅后又写了两个批语。不久，贺诚出任总后勤部第一副部长。"}],"contents":[{"id":"d0e0328da4","type":"title","text":"对贺诚来信的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"fdc972f641"},{"id":"3d47d5eb97","type":"paragraph","text":"贺诚同志来信请中央处理。我意应给予工作","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"fdc972f641"},{"id":"48ad7e7ddc","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"fdc972f641"},{"id":"5f566a5793","type":"paragraph","text":"七二年六月二十八日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"fdc972f641"}],"page":{"id":"a655278311","publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"fdc972f641","start":322,"end":322}}}},"__N_SSG":true}